Package: iarm
Type: Package
Title: Item Analysis in Rasch Models
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Marianne", "Mueller", email = "mllm@zhaw.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to assess model fit and identify misfitting items for Rasch models (RM) and partial credit models (PCM). Included are item fit statistics, item-restscore association, conditional likelihood ratio tests, assessment of measurement error, estimates of the reliability and test targeting.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), eRm
Imports:
    PP,
    psychotools,
    mRm,
    stats,
    utils,
Author: Marianne Mueller [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Marianne Mueller <mllm@zhaw.ch>
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
